problem_text_cn: 如图,平行四边形ABCD和平行四边形EBCF关于直线BC对称,且∠ABE=90°,则∠F的度数是()
problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, the parallelogram ABCD and the parallelogram EBCF are symmetric about the straight line BC, and ∠ABE = N_0, then the degree of ∠F is ()
raw_answer: 解:∵平行四边形ABCD和平行四边形EBCF关于直线BC对称,∴两个四边形全等,∴∠ABC=∠EBC,∵∠ABE=90°,∴∠EBC=45°,∵平行四边形对角相等,∴∠F=45°．故选:B．
